Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓犯人們移動到8號艙門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼  不過是一兩個原始星球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟能得到硫加相比較而言不就不值一提了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奧之院明明也知道這道理  到底為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！ 那個艙門是通往艦橋的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:17.04,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(340,280)\fad(1000,0)}最終
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8)\fs22}怪光事件1個月後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在東京海灣造成特大傷亡的迷之怪光事件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經過去了整整1個月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各國聯合調查團仍在受災地區進行現場勘察
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但至今還無法確定事件原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最終的失蹤者人數也未能得到統計
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是遭受衝擊後的六本木街區
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,過去人流不斷的繁華街區
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如您所見  成了現在一望無際的廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現場在二次災害後封鎖至今
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止一般人入內
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,政府的重建計劃也還沒有定案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的真田前輩也這樣報道著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事件已經造成了極大的損害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我們必須做些力所能及的事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fs22}第55回文化祭主題！！\N追蹤受災地區人們的生活！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  你們都有好好聽我說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  我們根本就不是報道研的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊  為什麼我們要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！難道說報道研的只有早宮和北村嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三年生在9月引退了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我也是被硬拉過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,具體就是那樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,收集現場人們的呼聲  然後做成報道的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,報道生命線還未恢復和困難人群的現狀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣還不如六本木廢墟的潛入取材呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  這樣就和我們的廢墟研相關了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有傳聞說事件是宇宙人所為哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊  而且呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還說偽裝成地球人住在各處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人罹難了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們怎麼還能只顧自己的興趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我的得意弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,北村你是第一次見吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有什麼事  室戶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  有點小事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs20\fad(100,500)}這樣你還堅持宇宙人不存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新作  簽名本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,定價1500日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優惠價1000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,買了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,活生生一個只顧興趣的反面教材
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,簡單來說就是祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在各個學校內盛大地…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以早宮在為此…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,餘興？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說誰是祭典餘興的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我自言自語…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你還故意咕嘟那麼大聲！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說對不起了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別和我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想讓別人覺得我認識你這樣的電波男
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}（電波：指不與人交流，或有妄想症的人群。\N本意是指腦袋中有其他人的聲音、思考、指示、妨害等以電波傳達的情況，\N簡單說就是幻聽症狀，但引申意義也很多。）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別說我電波
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是還放不下吧  中杉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  說過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點  千川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  文化祭一定要幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想說不想幫忙餘興節目？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這份心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  你那句話傷到我的少女心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人就算了  唯獨千川你一定得幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就說定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:06:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,掰掰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼關係  就去幫忙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不就是當事人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把東京搞得一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺就像被人說就是我們做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}功  還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你沒有好好把垃圾分類吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當時已經盡了最大努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我們不在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,何止是東京  地球人都已經全滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.03,0:07:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近覺得還是這樣子比較輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果處理得再好些  不用又和你二心同體就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:08:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那還不是功吸取了硫加才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了拯救中杉小夜香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.12,0:08:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你身體的損壞狀態可是接近再生臨界值哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能活著就要謝天謝地了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這我也明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  我是麥基烏斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪裡  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道阿特拉衛星監獄嗎  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,收押重犯的終生流放地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖分子金澤爾·豪瓦也被監禁在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前往那裡的押送船被囚犯們劫持了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,囚犯押送船嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是囚犯們和協助逃脫的嫌疑犯的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,斯·迪安謝路  原神祗官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿格拉茲涅·茲拉  原聯邦上議員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,法羅德·庫斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和他雙胞胎妹妹的塔塞拉·庫斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原盧梅基斯的生物化學工程的研究主任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特爾·格蘭是原情報部的作戰指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其部下莫斯·吉利是引導這次逃脫的嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個阿留多人  巴里克·尼瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是反政府組織的特工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但從這次越獄的計劃到實施都有參與
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是些來頭不小的囚犯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,罪名是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們就是從政府設施裡奪取硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,利用基加運送到了地球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,並想要試驗硫加的力量的幕後主謀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們已經潛入地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要毫髮無損地抓住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後遣返聯邦警察總部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪·希馮  這就是交給你的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把地球作為硫加實驗台的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人因為他們而死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  中杉同學也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,饒不了他們！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:11:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,砰  逮捕你的心吶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  Cut
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,OK  小紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝吶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝吶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  Good! Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小紫苑真是太美味了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  越智先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那毫無做作的天然正是小紫苑的魅力所在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然基本都是裝出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要你管呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您走好吶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在東京不是很沒生氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要靠小紫苑讓大家振奮起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…社長  打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒時間做這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有新任務…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是你的任務哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說這個  逃犯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:12:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你代墊的半年份房租
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你也想要情報的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是這樣沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好好幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以有田紫苑的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好不容易才給你建立起來的地球身份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你對「有田紫苑」太過敷衍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依露瑪女士  巨蛋哦巨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs17}（ドームですよドーム：出自天海春香的著名台詞「プロデューサーさん、○○○ですよ、○○○！」。\N巨蛋是指東京ドーム，位於東京都文京區後樂，愛稱是BIG EGG）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好  您儘管吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑最棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.82,0:12:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塔斯克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,15年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是14年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是何等…何等骯髒的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到處都是阿留多人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迪安謝路閣下  確實…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的相貌很像阿留多人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但他們是這個星球的原住民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還不是一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要藏在這等骯髒的星球  實在無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是很諷刺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經是作為硫加實驗場的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在又不得不偽裝成這個星球的原住民而潛伏在此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:43.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就憑你這下賤的傢伙也敢對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡就遵從我的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,擬態反應芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種邊境星球…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字叫尼諾·莫列路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是住在賓館的外國人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然不得不變成醜惡的阿留多人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能會很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘗試一次當這種劣等生物不也挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿留多人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個帶上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,軍人的話一定知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通訊機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和舊式的拉迪阿型用法相同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以用來聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今後與我聯絡時也用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實在是不愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迪安謝路閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是為了大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在這裡的期間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以爭取遮掩罪狀的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫斯  是你做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,政府內部的伙伴一定會證明上校你們所做的是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然化為阿留多人藏身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這女人的想法還真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  跟阿格拉茲涅議員您也挺合適嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只說一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成為地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各自的行為避免張揚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,融入地球人中的話危險就會降低
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  如果死了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個芯片就會將身體分解  完全消滅證據
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想讓地球人知道我們的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  我可不認為這個行星的原住民能殺得了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有一個預想外的因素  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼  巴里克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個將硫加封印的搜查官還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狂戰士殺手的巴迪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個依古西奧拉的阿留多人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過只有一個人還不是我們的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  為保險起見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時還是請各位安分地作為阿留多人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  作為地球人行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塔斯克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這亡命專家好像已經很上道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經還是個被稱為「伊茲達魯塔的蒼牙」的男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴里克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎也已經身染惡習了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  我可已經不是小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,學會了精明的處事之道罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  那個廢物還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大清早的做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還很睏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要擺脫那個老太婆才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去還可能影響任務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有田紫苑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想趁夜逃跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁夜逃跑該晚上做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情報和零花錢都沒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你最喜歡的飯團也吃不到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我的生活費可不夠巴迪的伙食費啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然宇宙船裡有我的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不像米飯那麼好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兩三天前入住到新宿的一家賓館中的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可別小看了阿留多人網路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男的名字叫尼諾·莫列路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,East Hotel  2105號房
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,據說是個法國美術商人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那可不是地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰…誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別太引人注意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:18:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尼諾·莫列路？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好慘…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殺人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殺人啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被人看到了！ 巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迪安謝路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡  2105號房
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別靠近  等警察來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,換我  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撞…撞到了！大哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,睡了一整晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的被車撞飛了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,車子都凹陷進去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生  請再認真檢查下！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你說要檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一點傷痕都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之腦部也正常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.87,0:20:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生  那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子  這孩子的性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看他這樣  完全不用擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功  別待太久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就此告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是出現頭部震顫症的話就再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  孩子  稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能這麼回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這之後怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃犯居然被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還有線索
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個項鏈一樣的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,調查那個的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是這麼笨手笨腳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.53,0:21:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就是依古西奧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}finally I lost the world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(100,1000)}true or false in world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:14.46,yugao,NTP,0,0,0,,好～偶是巴迪·希馮·阿魯提拉～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:18.39,yugao,NTP,0,0,0,,看來成人後的我真的成為了搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:19.30,yugao,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:23.05,yugao,NTP,0,0,0,,還有  沒想到能再見到那個那塔魯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.68,0:23:26.21,yugao,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔魯也變成不俗的男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.12,0:23:30.72,yugao,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  他好像被牽扯進了奇怪的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.85,0:23:31.96,yugao,NTP,0,0,0,,真擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:34.39,yugao,NTP,0,0,0,,未來的偶  加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.94,0:23:37.63,yugao,NTP,0,0,0,,白奧林  飯還沒好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:39.84,biaoti2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(350,285)}命運起伏
